dml.team5.antlr

Class ModifiedPLSQLBaseListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • dml.team5.antlr.ModifiedPLSQLBaseListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ModifiedPLSQLListener, org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener

    public class ModifiedPLSQLBaseListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements ModifiedPLSQLListener
    This class provides an empty implementation of ModifiedPLSQLListener, which can be extended to create a listener which only needs to handle a subset of the available methods.
